  Values are shown in cleartext and stored unencrypted on this host (0600). Saving applies them to  
  a RUNNING VM immediately; a stopped one gets them on its next start.                              
                                                                                                    
  Tip: name a GitHub token GH_TOKEN and put it under an [org dir] section (e.g. [github.com/acme])  
  to scope git auth to that subtree.                                                                
                                                                                                    
